Antinomy of Common Flowers - https://matcherino.com/tournaments/121200,sonofgod_1998,9 / 48,AoCF,https://v5.airtableusercontent.com/v3/u/33/33/1727546400000/4MzLti3n1IZnPpvLIJy3HQ/m2PCeWAqdEhcijM5xoR9qpWaUF54BkSxfJwr2moMIlQYmxvwVU4shPyOLkO1cM_vuxa0lCOYYkIcVyzdDnQ0Vp0TaE_XZvjGrJRWj8tUOq869xMIFXwxKO4kwpA0rH47d_Syz24fWL2yt9Za6dnTTA/hbbz3Vi46ZrkBju60zgqV74V0rvTS4tOUZoGPfghRZ8,https://matcherino.com/tournaments/121200,,3/5,,Winner must keep character. Loser may switch.,recGNnYHJ8VOGbN4t,unyu__,,"1.) Tom's Netplay Patch, improved delayed netcode for global connection: http://lunarcast.net/aocf.php You'll download the `Netplay.zip` (password netplay) and make an exception on the game's folder from Windows Defender or whatever anti-virus you have. Extract the contents in the game's folder and run `th155n.exe`. If all is done right (and your anti-virus didn't delete it), then you'll see a ""1.03ef"" besides the game's title bar. 
2.) To connect quickly, please use ProxyPunch (PP): https://github.com/delthas/proxypunch/releases/latest , know that these matches CAN'T be spectated but these will give the LEAST amount of lag compared to other forms of connecting without being able to host (Port Forward being the LEAST amount of lag and the best way to spectate as well)
3.) To be able to be seen on stream, Radmin VPN ( https://www.radmin-vpn.com/ ) will be used for those who can't host but would like to be seen on stream. Please know that this will give the MOST amount of lag out of all the options, but it will allow players to be spectated compared to not being able to thanks to ProxyPunch (PP)",,,,Any unintentional glitches will reset the entire match to keep it fair for everyone. Any intentional glitches will give the opponent the entire match win and potential for ban from any future tournaments (if they have been hiding this glitch to win),,,,,"Once 15 entrants have joined, +10 euro to the pool; once we reach 30 entrants... we'll see (still in the works)",,,
